@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+# CVE-2025-69228 — Already Fixed via CVE-2025-69227
+
+The fix for CVE-2025-69228 (moving `size = 0` out of the multipart while loop
+in `aiohttp/web_request.py`) is already incorporated into the CVE-2025-69227
+patch for aiohttp 3.12.15.
+
+CVE-2025-69227 refactors the same loop using the walrus operator and moves
+`size = 0` before the loop in the same hunk, making this patch a no-op.
+
+Status: not_affected (fix already present via CVE-2025-69227)

